		<title>小貓也愛看卡通！新手貓爸用平板顧毛孩　貓媽媽超傻眼 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/23/%e5%b0%8f%e8%b2%93%e4%b9%9f%e6%84%9b%e7%9c%8b%e5%8d%a1%e9%80%9a%ef%bc%81%e6%96%b0%e6%89%8b%e8%b2%93%e7%88%b8%e7%94%a8%e5%b9%b3%e6%9d%bf%e9%a1%a7%e6%af%9b%e5%ad%a9%e3%80%80%e8%b2%93%e5%aa%bd%e5%aa%bd/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 23 Sep 2025 06:03:53 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[時事]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[卡通]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[寵物]]></category>
